package.name: Ced_CsMarketplace
package.summary: CedCommerce Marketplace is a feature rich extension for transforming your E-commerce Store into a manageable Multi-Vendor Store like Amazon and Ebay.It has independent, uniquely designed and easy to use vendor panel to managevendor account, products, orders, transactions with advance reporting system.
package.description: CedCommerce Marketplace, a rich and powerful feature, is an open source extension for Magento ecommerce platform. It transforms your online store into a Multi Seller / Multi Vendor environment where the vendors will get a strong platform to sell their products and can reach out to a vast number of customers. The admin panel of Magento has been configured to include all the settings whereby all the vendors and their information can be managed, providing the Website Administrator with plenty of features to control the flow of the Marketplace. Vendors can create their shops in the main Marketplace and can handle their store by the easy to use magento admin panel dashboard. Cs-Marketplace provides the Vendors the ability to add products from their vendor panel, manage their products, view their respective products' orders that have been placed by the customers, see the transactions being done and the commission paid by the Website Admin to the Vendor. Moreover, the Vendors can also keep a track of the performance of their store with the help of analysis reports. At frontend, customers will be able to see the products provided by different sellers, but the products listed here will only be those that have been approved by the website admin from magento admin panel. Thus, the customers will have the feature of getting the product at competitive prices by different sellers. They can also order the products of multiple vendors. All the payments will be received by the website admin with the details properly listed in a tabular format, the website admin can then transfer the amount of commission to the respective vendors as and when needed.
package.notes: Stable Release -----What's New----- 1.) Add new feature Vendor search (by name,country,state and zip) on vendor's list page. 2.) Add new feature Category & Attribute filter on vendor's shop page. 3.) Improve Vendor Panel Design 4.) Minor bug fixes
